text: Thinley Dorji is an archer from Bhutan. Dorji competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics.Thinley DORJI He was born on 20 November 1950.Thinley Dorji == References == Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Bhutanese archers Category:Olympians for Bhutan
